        <updateDate>2004-12-23T16:41:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Truth in Trials Act - Amends the Controlled Substances Act to establish as an affirmative defense for any person facing prosecution or a proceeding for any marijuana-related offense that the marijuana-related activities in question were in compliance with State law regarding the medical use of marijuana. </p> <p>]]></text>
      </summary>
